        <num>CCP 737</num>
        <heading>737.  Partnership; partners</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 737.  Partnership; partners
A partnership has the procedural capacity to be sued in its partnership name.
The partners of an existing partnership may not be sued on a partnership obligation unless the partnership is joined as a defendant.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112237</p>
